{"tid":167924,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"電子電路問題","createTime":"2017-03-23T07:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T00:51:40.000Z","uid":39722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"291e205a07b3e449049197019accef4d3c2fa6d5","tid":167924,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"有冇人明改進電路b 有咩改善左？<br />\n上網睇話唔夠電都可以令三極管開關<br />\n但唔明個邏輯同點解要咁做，是否必須？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2i7s10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2i7s10.jpg&h=1a108fe7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b9eb56bf258e59277ad643b5ca37319e278233e","tid":167924,"uid":88236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"利申：9估<br />\n<br />\na,個device 用哂啲電，唔過bjt threshold.<br />\nb, q1 supply q2, 所以唔夠電都得"},{"pid":"2182e107d5c7c184199929d1fbb1f59b4959d34c","tid":167924,"uid":74096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"如果你load大，draw曬current, a個圖粒diodes唔夠力推去active region，咪oc左<br />\n但b 的q2, 就算你load draw曬大部分current, 剩設少少ic,q2都有力推q2, 造到complete circuit，咪開到<br />\n<br />\n利申：9估"},{"pid":"5809ed72621a6e0d0b26eb469bec37b364dc2a7f","tid":167924,"uid":88236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你load大，draw曬current, a個圖粒diodes唔夠力推去active region，咪oc左<br />\n但b 的q2, 就算你load draw曬大部分current, 剩設少少ic,q2都有力推q2, 造到complete circuit，咪開到<br />\n<br />\n利申：9估</blockquote><br />\nvoltage?<br />\ncurrent係同一個loop 係一樣"},{"pid":"12cdac8f23c22cf972f6abe962154e9488448338","tid":167924,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人明改進電路b 有咩改善左？<br />\n上網睇話唔夠電都可以令三極管開關<br />\n但唔明個邏輯同點解要咁做，是否必須？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2i7s10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2i7s10.jpg&h=1a108fe7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.838dz.com%2Fad%2FLoan%2F1585.html&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD55ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7405f4e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇勁人可以解釋到點解要b ?"},{"pid":"c7f67f458f9c6c40172ab2bf8c582526b0eaec81","tid":167924,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:04:43.000Z","msg":"觸發器條pin一般用IC 3v 推on/off<br />\n個Load靠5v行"},{"pid":"f4e615668d19b7830a2b57aabb51fb3552dbb658","tid":167924,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:10:17.000Z","msg":"B圖係NPN三極管<br />\n<br />\n左面果隻 觸發器B腳只要大過＞0.7v先著<br />\n<br />\n5v會由C腳流去E腳<br />\n<br />\n第2隻三極管 第一隻E腳駁住B腳＞0.7v 同時導通<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎請兩隻三極管通晒"},{"pid":"e1b5058ad25884145a633e45b28c8dcea3007d5a","tid":167924,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:11:40.000Z","msg":"我9up"},{"pid":"2400d341a6e3b8cc5a156300134a7516524e97cd","tid":167924,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>B圖係NPN三極管<br />\n<br />\n左面果隻 觸發器B腳只要大過＞0.7v先著<br />\n<br />\n5v會由C腳流去E腳<br />\n<br />\n第2隻三極管 第一隻E腳駁住B腳＞0.7v 同時導通<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎請兩隻三極管通晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解要多此一舉？有咩作用？"},{"pid":"5f2df2c2fce3ede1d484179c38440d354e0d55d7","tid":167924,"uid":20720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T08:35:59.000Z","msg":"b 個drive current可以細d<br />\n同埋high speed on/off<br />\nb個waveform會靚d"},{"pid":"84ea44260bc007ead87bfed2b1ace90977e2308f","tid":167924,"uid":93867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人明改進電路b 有咩改善左？<br />\n上網睇話唔夠電都可以令三極管開關<br />\n但唔明個邏輯同點解要咁做，是否必須？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2i7s10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2i7s10.jpg&h=1a108fe7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.838dz.com%2Fad%2FLoan%2F1585.html&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD55ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7405f4e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇勁人可以解釋到點解要b ?</blockquote><br />\n睇BJT 其實要睇Current 唔係睇voltage<br />\nA圖入面 Q1, Ic=<strong>B</strong>Ib<br />\n當<strong>B</strong>=100, 如果Ic=1, Ib=0.01<br />\n但好多時觸發器果邊只係logic, 出唔到咁大Current<br />\n所以B 圖入面多左隻Q2 with emitter follower config, 佢既用途係用黎俾補 current,所以觸發器果邊需要既Current 就會變得好細好細，所以普通logic gate 都可以drive 到"},{"pid":"3eb32b88f73c12284f6c17d17a11e534788e8030","tid":167924,"uid":93867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人明改進電路b 有咩改善左？<br />\n上網睇話唔夠電都可以令三極管開關<br />\n但唔明個邏輯同點解要咁做，是否必須？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2i7s10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2i7s10.jpg&h=1a108fe7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.838dz.com%2Fad%2FLoan%2F1585.html&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD55ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7405f4e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇勁人可以解釋到點解要b ?</blockquote><br />\n睇BJT 其實要睇Current 唔係睇voltage<br />\nA圖入面 Q1, Ic=<strong>B</strong>Ib<br />\n當<strong>B</strong>=100, 如果Ic=1, Ib=0.01<br />\n但好多時觸發器果邊只係logic, 出唔到咁大Current<br />\n所以B 圖入面多左隻Q2 with emitter follower config, 佢既用途係用黎俾補 current,所以觸發器果邊需要既Current 就會變得好細好細，所以普通logic gate 都可以drive 到</blockquote><br />\n寫錯左 Q1 Q2,交換返就ok"},{"pid":"f171e1cb764536af13265522826d12dee30673d1","tid":167924,"uid":39722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人明改進電路b 有咩改善左？<br />\n上網睇話唔夠電都可以令三極管開關<br />\n但唔明個邏輯同點解要咁做，是否必須？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2i7s10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2i7s10.jpg&h=1a108fe7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.838dz.com%2Fad%2FLoan%2F1585.html&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD55ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7405f4e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇勁人可以解釋到點解要b ?</blockquote><br />\n睇BJT 其實要睇Current 唔係睇voltage<br />\nA圖入面 Q1, Ic=<strong>B</strong>Ib<br />\n當<strong>B</strong>=100, 如果Ic=1, Ib=0.01<br />\n但好多時觸發器果邊只係logic, 出唔到咁大Current<br />\n所以B 圖入面多左隻Q2 with emitter follower config, 佢既用途係用黎俾補 current,所以觸發器果邊需要既Current 就會變得好細好細，所以普通logic gate 都可以drive 到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打，大致上都明白，仲有個問題，如果觸發果邊都只會係出好少電，咁個1k resistor又有乜用？ 點解b 圖唔洗在Q1 Q2各用一粒1k resistor?"},{"pid":"56f99c2c18ee8ac0c968eb63922d162558c56917","tid":167924,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T00:51:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人明改進電路b 有咩改善左？<br />\n上網睇話唔夠電都可以令三極管開關<br />\n但唔明個邏輯同點解要咁做，是否必須？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2i7s10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2i7s10.jpg&h=1a108fe7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.838dz.com%2Fad%2FLoan%2F1585.html&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD55ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7405f4e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.838dz.com/ad/Loan/1585.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇勁人可以解釋到點解要b ?</blockquote><br />\n睇BJT 其實要睇Current 唔係睇voltage<br />\nA圖入面 Q1, Ic=<strong>B</strong>Ib<br />\n當<strong>B</strong>=100, 如果Ic=1, Ib=0.01<br />\n但好多時觸發器果邊只係logic, 出唔到咁大Current<br />\n所以B 圖入面多左隻Q2 with emitter follower config, 佢既用途係用黎俾補 current,所以觸發器果邊需要既Current 就會變得好細好細，所以普通logic gate 都可以drive 到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打，大致上都明白，仲有個問題，如果觸發果邊都只會係出好少電，咁個1k resistor又有乜用？ 點解b 圖唔洗在Q1 Q2各用一粒1k resistor?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實正常生器果陣 Q1都要加隻1k<br />\n<br />\nProtect mcu 觸發器果d port <br />\n驚有reverse feedback"}]}